data-start=\"763\" data-end=\"775\">Tickets:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"895\">\r\n<li data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"811\">\r\n<p data-start=\"780\" data-end=\"811\">Available <strong data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"809\">at the entrance</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"895\">\r\n<p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"895\">Or buy now online here 👉 <strong data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"860\"><a class=\"\" href=\"../tickets/1\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"893\">Get Your Ticket</a></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"895\">\r\n<p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"895\">Don&rsquo;t miss the moment you&rsquo;ve been voting for &ndash; come and witness your chosen contestant shine before the nation!</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"895\">\r\n<p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"895\">Merci d&rsquo;avoir vot&eacute; et soutenu votre candidat pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute; dans la comp&eacute;tition Mulema Gospel.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1071\" data-end=\"1412\">Demain, c&rsquo;est l&rsquo;occasion de <strong data-start=\"1192\" data-end=\"1214\">les voir EN DIRECT</strong> sur sc&egrave;ne au <strong data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1249\">Palais des Sports</strong> de Yaound&eacute; lors du <strong data-start=\"1269\" data-end=\"1280\">Prime 1</strong> &ndash; une exp&eacute;rience d&rsquo;adoration vibrante o&ugrave; 53 candidats venus de tout le Cameroun &eacute;l&egrave;veront leurs voix en louange au Tr&egrave;s-Haut.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1502\"><strong data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1427\">Date :</strong> Demain</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1502\"><strong data-start=\"1440\" data-end=\"1451\">Heure :</strong> 15h00</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1502\"><strong data-start=\"1463\" data-end=\"1473\">Lieu :</strong> Palais des Sports, Yaound&eacute;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1502\"><strong data-start=\"1507\" data-end=\"1520\">Billets :</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1660\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1553\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1553\">Disponibles <strong data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1551\">&agrave; l&rsquo;entr&eacute;e</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1660\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1556\" data-end=\"1660\">Ou achetez-les d&egrave;s maintenant en ligne ici 👉 <a class=\"\" href=\"../tickets/1\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"1602\" data-end=\"1658\"><strong data-start=\"1603\" data-end=\"1625\">Acheter mon billet</strong></a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1773\">Ne manquez pas le moment pour lequel vous avez vot&eacute; &ndash; venez voir votre candidat briller devant la natio</p>', '<p><em data-start=\"1806\" data-end=\"1841\">Coordonnatrice IT du Mulema Gospel</em></p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1857\">Rokayatou</strong></p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-08-08 23:44:07', '2025-08-08 23:44:07'),
(16, 'Engr. Mbole', '1,58,59,70,71,76,77,82,83,84,85,86,87,88,89,90,91,92,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109,110,111,112,113,114,115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126,127,128,129,130,131,132,133,134,135,136,137,138,139,140,141,142,143,144,145,146,1396,1401,1785,1787,2058,2060,2065,2067,2068', NULL, '', 'Voting Resumed – Mulema Gospel Competition', '<p>Greetings in the name of our Lord.</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"187\" data-end=\"439\">It has pleased God that you are still part of the Mulema Gospel Competition. We are now in Week 2 with 35 contestants still in the running. As you are aware, the scoring breakdown remains as follows: Voting &ndash; 10%, Ambassadors &ndash; 30%, and Judges &ndash; 60%.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"441\" data-end=\"757\">On Saturday 9th, 20 contestants were eliminated from the Mulema House. Voting was temporarily disabled during this process, but we are pleased to inform you that <strong data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"634\">voting has now been resumed</strong>. Please note that voting will remain open until the eve of the next eliminations, after which it will be disabled again.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"759\" data-end=\"868\">We encourage you to continue engaging your supporters and ambassadors during this phase of the competition.</p>', '<p>Kind regards,<br data-start=\"883\" data-end=\"886\" /><strong data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"900\">Roukayatou</strong><br data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"903\" />IT Coordinator<br data-start=\"917\" data-end=\"920\" />Mulema Gospel Competition</p>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-11 11:31:47', '2025-08-11 11:32:42'),
(17, 'Engr. Mbole', '1,58,59,64,70,71,75,76,77,82,83,84,85,86,87,88,89,90,91,92,93,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109,110,111,112,113,114,115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126,127,128,129,130,131,132,133,134,135,136,137,138,139,140,141,142,143,144,145,146,1396,1401,1785,1787,2058,2060,2065,2067,2068', NULL, NULL, 'Reprise des votes – Compétition Mulema Gospel', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"183\" data-end=\"466\">Il a plu &agrave; Dieu que vous fassiez toujours partie de la comp&eacute;tition Mulema Gospel. Nous sommes maintenant dans la deuxi&egrave;me semaine avec 35 candidats encore en lice. Comme vous le savez, la r&eacute;partition des notes reste la suivante : Votes &ndash; 10 %, Ambassadeurs &ndash; 30 %, et Juges &ndash; 60 %.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"468\" data-end=\"830\">Le samedi 9, 20 candidats ont &eacute;t&eacute; &eacute;limin&eacute;s de la Maison Mulema. Les votes avaient &eacute;t&eacute; temporairement d&eacute;sactiv&eacute;s pendant ce processus, mais nous avons le plaisir de vous informer que <strong data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"688\">les votes sont d&eacute;sormais r&eacute;activ&eacute;s</strong>. Veuillez noter que les votes resteront ouverts jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; la veille des prochaines &eacute;liminations, apr&egrave;s quoi ils seront de nouveau d&eacute;sactiv&eacute;s.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"832\" data-end=\"952\">Nous vous encourageons &agrave; continuer de mobiliser vos soutiens et vos ambassadeurs durant cette phase de la comp&eacute;tition.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"954\" data-end=\"1043\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Cordialement,</p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"970\" data-end=\"984\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p>Coordinatrice Informatique</p>\r\n<p>Comp&eacute;tition Mulema Gospel</p>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-11 11:37:42', '2025-08-11 11:39:43'),
