,1918,1919,1920,1921,1922,1923,1924,1925,1926,1927,1928,1929,1930,1931,1932,1933,1934,1935,1936,1937,1938,1939,1940,1941,1942,1943,1944,1945,1946,1947,1948,1949,1950,1951,1952,1953,1954,1955,1956,1957,1958,1959,1960,1961,1962,1963,1964,1965,1966,1967,1968,1969,1970,1971,1972,1973,1974,1975,1976,1977,1978,1979,1980,1981,1982,1983,1984,1985,1986,1987,1988,1989,1990,1991,1992,1993,1994,1995,1996,1997,1998,1999,2000,2001,2002,2003,2004,2005,2006,2007,2008,2009,2010,2011,2012,2013,2014,2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,2020,2021,2022,2023,2024,2025,2026,2027,2028,2029,2030,2031,2032,2033,2034,2035,2036,2037,2038,2039,2040,2041,2042,2043,2044,2045,2046,2047,2048,2049,2050,2051,2052,2053,2054,2055,2056,2057,2059,2061,2062,2063,2064,2066,2069,2070', NULL, '', 'Reprise des votes  – Mulema Gospel Competition', NULL, '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\">Nous avons le plaisir de vous informer que <strong data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"397\">les votes pour la comp&eacute;tition Mulema Gospel ont officiellement repris</strong>. Votre vote joue un r&ocirc;le essentiel pour soutenir votre candidat pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;, car il repr&eacute;sente 10 % de la note totale, aux c&ocirc;t&eacute;s des &eacute;valuations des Ambassadeurs (30 %) et des Juges (60 %).</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\"><br data-start=\"597\" data-end=\"600\" />We are pleased to inform you that <strong data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"701\">voting for the Mulema Gospel Competition has officially resumed</strong>. Your vote plays a vital role in supporting your favourite contestant, as it contributes 10% to the overall score, alongside the evaluations of Ambassadors (30%) and Judges (60%).</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\">Nous vous encourageons &agrave; voter d&egrave;s maintenant et &agrave; inviter d&rsquo;autres personnes &agrave; faire de m&ecirc;me. Les votes resteront ouverts jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; la veille des prochaines &eacute;liminations, apr&egrave;s quoi ils seront de nouveau d&eacute;sactiv&eacute;s.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\">We encourage you to cast your votes now and invite others to do the same. Voting will remain open until the eve of the next eliminations, after which it will be disabled again.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\">Merci pour votre soutien constant qui contribue au succ&egrave;s de cette comp&eacute;tition.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"883\">Thank you for your continued support in making this competition a success.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1563\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Cordialement</p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1487\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p>Coordinatrice Informatique</p>\r\n<p>Mulema Gospel Competition</p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-08-11 11:53:42', '2025-08-11 11:53:42'),
(19, 'Mbole', '20250811055324Staff_List1.csv', NULL, NULL, '📢 Extraordinary Online Meeting on the Return Match Versus Acha Hospital Annex Bamenda📢', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">Following our recent announcement regarding the return leg of our football match against Acha Hospital Annex Bamenda scheduled for <strong data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"639\">Saturday, 16th August 2025</strong>, it is imperative that we assess our current financial standing before confirming the fixture.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">I am therefore convening an <strong data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"803\">Extraordinary Online EXCO Meeting</strong> on <strong data-start=\"807\" data-end=\"863\">Wednesday, 13th August 2025, from 7:00 PM to 8:00 PM</strong> via Google Meet.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"901\">🔗 Meeting Link:</strong> <a class=\"\" href=\"https://meet.google.com/myy-ixki-gzy\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"978\">https://meet.google.com/myy-ixki-gzy</a></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong data-start=\"1048\" data-end=\"1059\">Agenda:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Review of contributions received so far.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Analysis of whether the available funds meet the budgeted requirement of 200,000 FCFA.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Decision on whether to proceed with or postpone the scheduled match.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Any other business.<br /></strong>Your punctual attendance and active participation are critical to ensuring that our decision reflects both our financial realities and the club&rsquo;s long-term interests.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">Thank you for your dedication and continued commitment to Nkwen Baptist Center FC.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1556\" data-end=\"1609\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Best Regards</p>\r\n<p>Tefu R. Mbole</p>\r\n<p>N.B.C Football Club</p>\r\n<p>CC: Mr. Suiyka Enoch, Mr. Methuselah&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'csv', '2025-08-11 17:53:24', '2025-08-11 17:53:50'),
(20, 'Papa Rolly', '20250811055730Staff_List.csv', NULL, NULL, '📢 Extraordinary Online Meeting on the Return Match Versus Acha Hospital Annex Bamenda📢', NULL, '<p></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">Following our recent announcement regarding the return leg of our football match against Acha Hospital Annex Bamenda scheduled for <strong data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"639\">Saturday, 16th August 2025</strong>, it is imperative that we assess our current financial standing before confirming the fixture.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">I am therefore convening an <strong data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"803\">Extraordinary Online EXCO Meeting</strong> on <strong data-start=\"807\" data-end=\"863\">Wednesday, 13th August 2025, from 7:00 PM to 8:00 PM</strong> via Google Meet.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"901\">🔗 Meeting Link:</strong> <a class=\"\" href=\"https://meet.google.com/myy-ixki-gzy\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"978\">https://meet.google.com/myy-ixki-gzy</a></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong data-start=\"1048\" data-end=\"1059\">Agenda:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Review of contributions received so far.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Analysis of whether the available funds meet the budgeted requirement of 200,000 FCFA.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Decision on whether to proceed with or postpone the scheduled match.</strong></li>\r\n<li data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\"><strong>Any other business.<br /></strong>Your punctual attendance and active participation are critical to ensuring that our decision reflects both our financial realities and the club&rsquo;s long-term interests.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"736\">Thank you for your dedication and continued commitment to Nkwen Baptist Center FC.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1556\" data-end=\"1609\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Best Regards</p>\r\n<p>Tefu R. Mbole</p>\r\n<p>N.B.C Football Club</p>\r\n<p>CC: Mr. Suiyka Enoch, Mr. Methuselah&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'csv', '2025-08-11 17:57:30', '2025-08-11 17:57:30');
