2732,2733,2734,2735,2736,2737,2738,2739,2740,2741,2742,2743,2744,2745,2746,2747,2748,2749,2750,2751,2752,2753,2754,2755,2756,2757,2758,2759,2760,2761,2762,2763,2764,2765,2766,2767,2768,2769,2770,2771,2772,2773,2774,2775,2776,2777,2778,2779,2780,2781,2782,2783,2784,2785,2786,2787,2788,2789,2790,2791,2792,2793,2794,2795,2796,2797,2798,2799,2800,2801,2802,2803,2804,2805,2806,2807,2808,2809,2810,2811,2812,2813,2814,2815,2816,2817,2818,2819,2820,2821,2822,2823,2824', NULL, '', '🎶PRIME 2 est arrivé – Entrée gratuite au Palais des Sports !🎶', '<p><strong data-start=\"85\" data-end=\"153\">🎶MULEMA GOSPEL PRIME 2 est arriv&eacute; &ndash; Entr&eacute;e gratuite au Palais des Sports !🎶&nbsp;L&rsquo;&eacute;v&eacute;nement commence &agrave; 15h00 pr&eacute;cises.</strong></p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">Aujourd&rsquo;hui, c&rsquo;est <strong data-start=\"245\" data-end=\"256\">PRIME 2</strong> au <strong data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"292\">Palais des Sports de Yaound&eacute;</strong> !&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">Parmi les 34 candidats restants, 15 quitteront la maison Mulema ce soir.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">Les votes ne sont plus visibles, mais ils continuent jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; <strong data-start=\"441\" data-end=\"450\">12h00</strong>, apr&egrave;s quoi le syst&egrave;me n&rsquo;acceptera plus de votes.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">=&gt;Vos votes comptent (10%), avec</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">=&gt; Ceux des juges (60%) et des</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">=&gt; Ambassadeurs (30%).</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"200\" data-end=\"583\">✨ <strong data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"631\">Bonne nouvelle : l&rsquo;entr&eacute;e est GRATUITE !</strong> Venez vivre cette soir&eacute;e inoubliable de louange et de culture, et voir sur sc&egrave;ne les candidats pour lesquels vous avez vot&eacute;.</p>', '<p>Roukayatou</p>\r\n<p>Coordinatrice IT</p>\r\n<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-08-17 06:35:22', '2025-08-17 06:35:22'),
(28, 'Engr. Mbole', '1,58,70,71,75,76,77,82,83,84,85,86,87,88,89,90,91,92,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109,110,111,112,113,114,115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126,127,128,129,130,131,132,133,134,135,136,137,138,139,140,141,142,143,144,145,146,1396,1785,1787,2058,2067,2068,2337,2338,2355,2357,2358,2359,2360,2367,2368,2485,2486', NULL, NULL, 'Today is PRIME 2 at the Palais des Sports, Yaoundé!', NULL, '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">Out of the 34 remaining contestants, 15 will be leaving the Mulema House tonight.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">=&gt;Votes are no longer visible, but voting continues until <strong data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1347\">12:00 noon</strong>, after which the system will no longer accept votes.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">=&gt; Your votes count (10%), alongside the</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">=&gt; Judges (60%) and</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">=&gt; mbassadors (30%).</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1478\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1680\"><span data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1523\">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1523\">The event starts at exactly 3:00 PM.</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1680\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1680\"><br data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1526\" />✨ <strong data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1557\">Good news: Entry is FREE!</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1680\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1680\">Come witness this unforgettable evening of worship and culture, and support live on stage the contestants you voted for.</p>', '<p>Roukayatou</p>\r\n<p>Coordinatrice IT</p>\r\n<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-17 06:46:19', '2025-08-17 06:52:03'),
(29, 'Engr. Mbole', '20250817032013Nkwen staff list.csv', NULL, NULL, 'Letter of Appreciation – NBC FC 4–1 Acha Annex', '<p>NBC FC: Faith Fitness and Followship. (F3)</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"52\" data-end=\"64\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"66\" data-end=\"233\">Congratulations on a brilliant 4&ndash;1 victory. Captain <strong data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"127\">Berto</strong> led from the front with a superb <strong data-start=\"161\" data-end=\"174\">hat-trick</strong>, and the entire squad showed heart, discipline, and unity.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"435\">Special appreciation to <strong data-start=\"259\" data-end=\"280\">Senior Coach Levy</strong>. Your game plan worked perfectly, and you now maintain a <strong data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"361\">100% winning record</strong>. Thank you for preparing the boys so well and keeping our identity clear.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"623\">We also salute <strong data-start=\"452\" data-end=\"476\">Dr. David, Methu, Di, Mr. Bayond, Mr. Silas, Mr. Eugine&nbsp;</strong>and every committee member for tireless support before, during, and after the match. Your work off the pitch makes success on the pitch possible.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"657\">We are grateful to our partners:</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"658\" data-end=\"789\">\r\n<li data-start=\"658\" data-end=\"740\">\r\n<p data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"740\"><strong data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"699\">Nkwen Baptist Center Administration</strong> for <strong data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"738\">5 pallets of Super Monde water</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"789\">\r\n<p data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"789\"><strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"757\">DHS Office</strong> for a token of <strong data-start=\"773\" data-end=\"789\">25,000 F CFA</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"905\">Thank you to our fans for the constant encouragement. Let&rsquo;s recover well, stay humble, and build on this momentum.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"905\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"922\">Onward, NBC FC.</p>', '<p>Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"961\">Engr. T. R. Mbole</strong></p>\r\n<p>President,</p>\r\n<p>Nkwen Baptist Center FC</p>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'csv', '2025-08-17 15:20:13', '2025-08-17 15:21:18'),
(30, 'Engr. Mbole', '2337,2354,2355,2359', NULL, '59,76', 'Appreciation for Your Dedication and Excellence – Prime 2', '<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '<p data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"390\">Prime 2 has come to a close, and while 15 contestants must now leave the competition, we cannot overlook the excellence, wisdom, and fairness you have shown throughout this phase.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"390\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"390\">Your commitment, patience, and dedication to evaluating each performance with integrity has been truly inspiring. You have not only ensured that the competition remains credible but also uplifted the contestants by giving them valuable feedback and encouragement.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"390\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"874\">On behalf of the entire Mulema Gospel Talent Show team, I extend our heartfelt gratitude for the wonderful work you have done. We deeply appreciate the sacrifices of your time and energy in service of this vision.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"876\" data-end=\"930\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>With appreciation,</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"894\" data-end=\"897\" /><strong data-start=\"897\" data-end=\"911\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"911\" data-end=\"914\" />IT Coordinator</p>\r\n<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '202508171015291755465267703The Mulema GC-18.pdf', 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-17 22:15:29', '2025-08-17 22:15:51'),
(31, 'Mbole', '2065,2315,2357,2358,2360', NULL, '1,59,70', 'Remerciements pour Votre Dévouement et Votre Excellence – Prime 2', '<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1006\" data-end=\"1218\">Le Prime 2 s&rsquo;est achev&eacute; et, bien que 15 candidats quittent d&eacute;sormais la comp&eacute;tition, nous ne pouvons passer sous silence l&rsquo;excellence, la sagesse et l&rsquo;impartialit&eacute; dont vous avez fait preuve durant cette phase.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1006\" data-end=\"1218\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1532\">Votre engagement, votre patience et votre d&eacute;vouement &agrave; &eacute;valuer chaque prestation avec int&eacute;grit&eacute; sont une v&eacute;ritable source d&rsquo;inspiration. Vous avez non seulement garanti la cr&eacute;dibilit&eacute; de la comp&eacute;tition, mais vous avez &eacute;galement encourag&eacute; les candidats en leur offrant des remarques constructives et motivantes.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1532\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1534\" data-end=\"1792\">Au nom de toute l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe du Mulema Gospel Talent Show, nous vous exprimons notre profonde gratitude pour le travail exceptionnel que vous avez accompli. Nous appr&eacute;cions sinc&egrave;rement le sacrifice de votre temps et de votre &eacute;nergie au service de cette vision.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1534\" data-end=\"1792\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1794\" data-end=\"1852\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Avec reconnaissance,</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1814\" data-end=\"1817\" /><strong data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1831\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1831\" data-end=\"1834\" />Coordinatrice IT</p>\r\n<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '202508171018281755465424624The Mulema GC-18.pdf', 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-17 22:18:28', '2025-08-17 22:18:48');
