30,2731,2732,2733,2734,2735,2736,2737,2738,2739,2740,2741,2742,2743,2744,2745,2746,2747,2748,2749,2750,2751,2752,2753,2754,2755,2756,2757,2758,2759,2760,2761,2762,2763,2764,2765,2766,2767,2768,2769,2770,2771,2772,2773,2774,2775,2776,2777,2778,2779,2780,2781,2782,2783,2784,2785,2786,2787,2788,2789,2790,2791,2792,2793,2794,2795,2796,2797,2798,2799,2800,2801,2802,2803,2804,2805,2806,2807,2808,2809,2810,2811,2812,2813,2814,2815,2816,2817,2818,2819,2820,2821,2822,2823,2824,2825,2826,2827,2828,2829,2830,2831,2832,2833,2834,2835,2836,2837,2838,2839,2840,2841,2842,2843,2844,2845,2846,2847,2848', NULL, '', 'Les Votes Ont Repris : Qui Allez-Vous Sauver ? (Voting Resumes: Who Will You Save?)', '<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"898\">Merci pour votre soutien et pour tous les votes d&eacute;j&agrave; exprim&eacute;s. Demain matin, <strong data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"748\">15 candidats quitteront la Maison Mulema</strong>. Sur plus de <strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"813\">600 auditionn&eacute;s dans les 10 r&eacute;gions du Cameroun</strong>, nous sommes pass&eacute;s &agrave; <strong data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"853\">60 finalistes</strong>, et il ne reste plus que <strong data-start=\"879\" data-end=\"895\">20 candidats</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"898\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"1060\">Qui reste et qui part d&eacute;pend d&eacute;sormais de <strong data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"955\">vos votes</strong>. Les votes ont repris&mdash;faites entendre votre voix et gardez votre candidat pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute; dans la comp&eacute;tition.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"1060\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"1060\"></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"137\" data-end=\"393\">Thank you for the support and the votes you have cast so far. Tomorrow morning, 15 contestants will be leaving the Mulema House. From over <strong data-start=\"276\" data-end=\"328\">600 auditioned across the 10 regions of Cameroon</strong>, we came down to <strong data-start=\"346\" data-end=\"362\">60 finalists</strong>, and now only <strong data-start=\"377\" data-end=\"390\">20 remain</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"137\" data-end=\"393\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"395\" data-end=\"545\">Who stays and who goes next is in <strong data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"443\">your hands</strong>. Voting has now resumed&mdash;make your votes count and keep your favorite contestant in the competition.</p>', '<p>Avec reconnaissance,&nbsp;With appreciation,</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1082\" data-end=\"1085\" /><strong data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1099\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1099\"><br data-start=\"1273\" data-end=\"1276\" /><em data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1304\">Coordinatrice Informatique</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1099\"><em data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1304\">Mulema Gospel</em></strong></p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-08-17 23:01:38', '2025-08-17 23:01:38'),
(33, 'Engr. Mbole', '84,89,97,101,103,105,111,112,117,119,124,127,128,130,134,135,141,142,143', NULL, '1,59,76,77', 'Félicitations pour avoir atteint la Prime 3 ! (Congratulations on Reaching Prime 3!)', '<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"1055\">F&eacute;licitations pour avoir atteint la <strong data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"916\">Prime 3</strong> ! 🎉 C&rsquo;est une belle &eacute;tape, mais rappelez-vous&mdash;ce n&rsquo;est pas la fin. Le plus grand objectif est encore devant vous, et chaque pas compte.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"1055\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1109\">Votre progression &agrave; travers la Prime 3 d&eacute;pend de :</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1109\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1110\" data-end=\"1179\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1110\" data-end=\"1130\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1130\"><strong data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1128\">Votes : 10 %</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1110\" data-end=\"1130\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1151\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1151\"><strong data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1149\">Juges : 60 %</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1151\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1179\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1179\"><strong data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1177\">Ambassadeurs : 30 %</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1179\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1368\">Restez concentr&eacute;s, donnez le meilleur de vous-m&ecirc;mes lors des r&eacute;p&eacute;titions et des prestations, et encouragez vos supporters &agrave; voter. Chaque effort compte pour votre chemin vers le sommet.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1368\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1368\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"420\">Congratulations on making it to <strong data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"297\">Prime 3</strong>! 🎉 This is a great milestone, but remember&mdash;this is not the end. The bigger goal is still ahead, and every step matters.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"420\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"422\" data-end=\"471\">How you make it through Prime 3 will depend on:</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"422\" data-end=\"471\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"535\">\r\n<li data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"490\">\r\n<p data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"490\"><strong data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"488\">Votes: 10%</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"490\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"491\" data-end=\"510\">\r\n<p data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"510\"><strong data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"508\">Judges: 60%</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"491\" data-end=\"510\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"535\">\r\n<p data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"535\"><strong data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"533\">Ambassadors: 30%</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"535\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"537\" data-end=\"697\">Stay focused, give your best in rehearsals and performances, and encourage your supporters to keep voting. Every effort counts toward your journey to the top.</p>', '<p>Avec encouragement,</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1392\" /><strong data-start=\"1392\" data-end=\"1406\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1406\" data-end=\"1409\" /><em data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1437\">Coordinatrice Informatique</em></p>\r\n<p><em data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1437\">Mulema Gospel</em></p>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'user', '2025-08-17 23:13:38', '2025-08-17 23:14:45'),
