,3130,3131,3132,3133,3134,3135,3136,3137', NULL, '', 'Important Announcement: Voting Update & Free Entry to Today’s Event at 3:00 PM (Annonce Importante : Mise à jour du vote & Entrée gratuite à l’événement d’aujourd’hui à)', '<p>MULEMA GOSPEL SEASON 1</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"106\">🇬🇧 English Version</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"131\" data-end=\"287\">As you might have noticed, the votes on the platform are now invisible, but voting is still ongoing. Voting will officially close today at <strong data-start=\"270\" data-end=\"284\">12:00 noon</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"131\" data-end=\"287\">The evaluation criteria are as follows:</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"394\">\r\n<li data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"349\">\r\n<p data-start=\"333\" data-end=\"349\"><strong data-start=\"333\" data-end=\"342\">Votes</strong>: 10%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"350\" data-end=\"369\">\r\n<p data-start=\"352\" data-end=\"369\"><strong data-start=\"352\" data-end=\"362\">Judges</strong>: 60%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"370\" data-end=\"394\">\r\n<p data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"394\"><strong data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"387\">Ambassadors</strong>: 30%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"533\">We are pleased to inform you that <strong data-start=\"430\" data-end=\"464\">entry to Prime 3 is free</strong>.<br data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"468\" />📍 Venue: Palais des Sports Complex, Yaound&eacute;<br data-start=\"512\" data-end=\"515\" />🕒 Time: 3:00 PM</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"533\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"533\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"533\"></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"540\" data-end=\"565\">🇫🇷 French Version</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"783\">Comme vous l&rsquo;avez remarqu&eacute;, les votes sur la plateforme sont d&eacute;sormais invisibles, mais le processus de vote continue toujours. Les votes prendront fin aujourd&rsquo;hui &agrave; <strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"780\">12h00 pr&eacute;cises</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"783\">Les crit&egrave;res d&rsquo;&eacute;valuation sont les suivants :</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"899\">\r\n<li data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"852\">\r\n<p data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"852\"><strong data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"844\">Votes</strong> : 10%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"872\">\r\n<p data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"872\"><strong data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"864\">Juges</strong> : 60%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"899\">\r\n<p data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"899\"><strong data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"891\">Ambassadeurs</strong> : 30%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"1058\">Nous avons le plaisir de vous informer que <strong data-start=\"944\" data-end=\"997\">l&rsquo;entr&eacute;e &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;v&eacute;nement d&rsquo;aujourd&rsquo;hui est gratuite</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"1058\">📍 Lieu : Palais des Sports, Yaound&eacute;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"1058\">🕒 Heure : 15h00</p>', '<p>Cordialement,</p>\r\n<p><strong data-start=\"1397\" data-end=\"1411\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1411\" data-end=\"1414\" />Coordinatrice IT</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1433\" /><em data-start=\"1433\" data-end=\"1466\">Mulema Gospel Talent &ndash; Saison 1</em></p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-08-23 10:56:34', '2025-08-23 10:56:34');
