,3130,3131,3132,3133,3134,3135,3136,3137,3138,3139,3140,3141,3142,3143,3144,3145,3146,3147,3148,3149,3150,3151,3152,3153,3154,3155,3156,3157,3158,3159,3160,3161,3162,3163,3164,3165,3166,3167,3168,3169,3170,3171,3172,3173,3174,3175,3176,3177,3178,3179,3180,3181,3182,3183,3184,3185,3186,3187,3188,3189,3190,3191,3192,3193,3194,3195,3196,3197,3198,3199,3200,3201,3202,3203,3204,3205,3206,3207,3208,3209,3210,3211,3212,3213,3214,3215,3216,3217,3218,3219,3220,3221,3222,3223,3224,3225,3226,3227,3228,3229,3230,3231,3232,3233,3234,3235,3236,3237,3238,3239,3240,3241,3242,3243,3244,3245,3246,3247,3248,3249,3250,3251,3252,3253,3254,3255,3256,3257,3258,3259,3260,3261,3262,3263,3264,3265,3266,3267,3268,3269,3270,3271,3272,3273,3274,3275,3276,3277,3278,3279,3280,3281,3282,3283,3284,3285,3286,3287,3288,3289,3290,3291,3292,3293,3294,3295,3296,3297,3298,3299,3300,3301,3302,3303,3304,3305,3306,3307,3308,3309,3310,3311,3312,3313,3314,3315,3316,3317,3318,3319,3320,3321,3322,3323,3324,3325,3326,3327,3328,3329,3330,3331,3332,3333,3334,3335,3336,3337,3338,3339,3340,3341,3342,3343', NULL, NULL, 'Happy New Month', '<p>Mulema Gospel</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">Wishing you a joyful and fruitful new month! Thank you sincerely for being part of <strong data-start=\"211\" data-end=\"235\">Mulema Gospel Talent</strong>. Because of your support, Season One was a success and came to a glorious end last Saturday, 30th August 2025, at the <strong data-start=\"354\" data-end=\"375\">Palais des Sports</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">A big congratulations once again to our winners:</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">🥇 Emmanuel Maballi &ndash; First Place</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">🥈 Onguene Mekana Glaube &ndash; Second Place</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">🥉 Mvogo Azielle &ndash; Third Place</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">This is not the end but only the beginning. Season One has closed, but the journey continues&mdash;get ready, because we look forward to welcoming you in <strong data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"709\">MGT Season Two</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"378\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"714\" data-end=\"783\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"860\"><strong data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"858\">Bonne nouvelle mois&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"860\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"1130\">Nous te souhaitons un mois rempli de joie et de b&eacute;n&eacute;dictions ! Merci sinc&egrave;rement d&rsquo;avoir fait partie de <strong data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"990\">Mulema Gospel Talent</strong>. Gr&acirc;ce &agrave; ton soutien, la Saison Une a &eacute;t&eacute; un v&eacute;ritable succ&egrave;s et s&rsquo;est achev&eacute;e en beaut&eacute; le samedi 30 ao&ucirc;t 2025 au <strong data-start=\"1106\" data-end=\"1127\">Palais des Sports</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"1130\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1281\">F&eacute;licitations encore une fois &agrave; nos laur&eacute;ats :</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1281\"><br data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1181\" />🥇 Emmanuel Maballi &ndash; Premier</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1281\"><br data-start=\"1210\" data-end=\"1213\" />🥈 Onguene Mekana Glaube &ndash; Deuxi&egrave;me</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1281\"><br data-start=\"1248\" data-end=\"1251\" />🥉 Mvogo Azielle &ndash; Troisi&egrave;me</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1281\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1463\">Ce n&rsquo;est pas la fin mais seulement le d&eacute;but. La Saison Une est termin&eacute;e, mais l&rsquo;aventure continue&mdash;pr&eacute;pare-toi, car nous avons h&acirc;te de te retrouver pour la <strong data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1460\">Saison Deux de MGT</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1546\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Avec gratitude,</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1483\" /><strong data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1497\">Roukayatou</strong></p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1497\" data-end=\"1500\" />Coordinatrice Informatique</p>\r\n<p><br data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1529\" /><em data-start=\"1529\" data-end=\"1544\">Mulema Gospel</em></p>', NULL, 0, 1, 1, 'customer', '2025-09-01 18:26:18', '2025-09-01 18:27:22');
